      <h1>Swim Lesson Scholarships &amp; Financial Assistance</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">A parent's guide to organizations that help make swim lessons affordable for every family.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <div class="intro-callout">
      <p>Cost should never be the reason a child doesn't learn to swim. Multiple national organizations offer scholarships, grants, and financial assistance to help families access swim lessons — many at no cost at all. We've compiled the most established programs in one place so you can find the right fit for your family.</p>
    </div>

