      <p>Live Like Jake has awarded more than 3,800 scholarships nationwide. Their scholarships are designed for families who cannot afford the cost of ISR lessons, which typically run $150–$250 per week for a six-week program. The foundation also operates an indoor swim facility in Palm Beach Gardens, FL.</p>

